Recommends: iperf3
Description: SecuBox Network Diagnostics — Troubleshooting Tools
 Network diagnostics module for SecuBox providing various troubleshooting
 tools including ping, traceroute, DNS lookup, WHOIS, MTR, port scanning,
 and network interface analysis.
 .
 Features:
  - Ping with RTT statistics
  - Traceroute with hop analysis
  - DNS lookup (A, AAAA, MX, NS, TXT, CNAME, SOA)
  - WHOIS domain/IP lookup
  - MTR (My Traceroute)
  - Port scanning (local network only)
  - Network interface listing
  - Routing table display
  - ARP table
  - Active connections (netstat-like)
  - Bandwidth testing (iperf3)
 .
 Part of SecuBox Debian edition.
